## 🎯 What it does

An AI-powered recruiter assistant that analyzes your resume and GitHub profile, finds the most relevant recruiters, ranks them by fit, and sends personalized messages — all automatically via MCP.

---

## ⚡ How it works

```
Resume + GitHub Username
        ↓
Claude analyzes both
        ↓
Finds relevant recruiters (LinkedIn)
        ↓
Ranks recruiters by relevance
        ↓
Writes custom message for each
        ↓
Sends message on LinkedIn (coming soon)
```

