## 🧠 What Claude analyzes from your resume

- Skills and tech stack
- Years of experience
- Projects built
- Education background
- Job titles targeted
- Gaps to address

---

## 🐙 What Claude analyzes from GitHub

- Programming languages used
- Repository quality and activity
- Commit consistency
- Project types (AI, web, backend etc.)
- Daily commit streak
- Overall developer activity score

---

## 🎯 How recruiter ranking works

Claude scores each recruiter based on:

| Factor | Weight |
|--------|--------|
| Matching tech stack | High |
| Company size fit | Medium |
| Role relevance | High |
| Location match | Medium |
| Recent hiring activity | High |

Top ranked recruiters get the most personalized messages.

---

## ✍️ Custom message formula

Each message is personalized using:
- Recruiter's name and company
- Specific role they hire for
- Your matching skills from resume
- Your strongest GitHub projects
- A clear ask (coffee chat / referral / application)

No copy-paste templates. Every message is unique. 🎯

